						   receive a message to buy your item!

						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-4">
					<div class="service-item">
						<div class="icon"><i class="fa fa-gear"></i></div>
						<h3>Buy the item you want!</h3>
						<p>Have you just received a message from a seller? Or, maybe you want to buy something but you are not so sure about what? Log in BuyOnTheFly to find out which items are being sold and...be the fastest! Our policy is "First Come First Served"!
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-4">
					<div class="service-item">
						<div class="icon"><i class="fa fa-life-ring"></i></div>
						<h3>Collect the item!</h3>
						<p>Have you just bought an item? Very well! You can pick up your item in one of the boxes located in the city where you live. The location of the right box will sent directly to you once the transaction has been completed!
						</p>
					</div>
