		<div class="container">
			<header>
				<h2>Get in Touch</h2>
				<p>Our headquarter is situated nearby the VU University Amsterdam as we are students. Feel free to contact us by filling in the form in the bottom of the page for any issue you deal with.
				</p>
			</header>
			<div class="map-wrapper">
				<div class="map-canvas" id="map-canvas">Loading map...</div>
