							The Netherlands
						</p>
					</address>
					<address>
						<span>Email</span>
						<p>mailbuyonthefly@gmail.com</p>
					</address>
					<address>
						<span>Phone</span>
						<p>+31 123-456-78900</p>
					</address>
				</div>
